### Material Supplier Prices API Tests
### Requires authentication token

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Material Supplier Prices Overview for a Material
# Replace {material_id} with actual material ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/materials/1/supplier-prices/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. List all Material Supplier Prices (optional filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. List Material Supplier Prices filtered by material
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/?material_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. List Material Supplier Prices filtered by supplier
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/?supplier_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create a new Material Supplier Price
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "material": 1,
  "supplier": 1,
  "price": 12.50,
  "valid_from": "2025-11-27",
  "note": "Mindestbestellmenge: 10 St√ºck"
}

### 6. Get specific Material Supplier Price details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Update a Material Supplier Price
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 11.99,
  "note": "Neuer Preis nach Preisverhandlung"
}

### 8. Delete a Material Supplier Price
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/material-supplier-prices/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
